  "prompt": "How is the movie \"Happy New Year\"?",
  "response": "\"Happy New Year\" is a Bollywood film that was released in 2014. Directed by Farah Khan, it features a star-studded cast including Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone, Abhishek Bachchan, Sonu Sood, Boman Irani, and Vivaan Shah. The movie revolves around a group of six losers who participate in a dance competition as a cover for their heist plan.\n\nThe film received mixed reviews from critics. While some praised the performances, particularly Shah Rukh Khan and Deepika Padukone, as well as the film's entertainment value, others criticized it for its predictable plot and lack of originality. However, it was a commercial success and performed well at the box office.\n\nIf you enjoy light-hearted, masala entertainers with dance, drama, and comedy, \"Happy New Year\" might be a fun watch.",
